{"type":"text","timestamp":1773352228147,"sessionID":"ses_31c010c9effeOfeCSqmf0ROAdl","part":{"id":"prt_ce4075c87001pXw9lCrd8mHdHU","sessionID":"ses_31c010c9effeOfeCSqmf0ROAdl","messageID":"msg_ce407543a001bNvttroHZdEBWv","type":"text","text":"Everything passes. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Implementation Summary\n\n### Commit 1: `feat(dynamic-agent-types): add agent registry client and format converter`\n\n**New files:**\n- **`src/lib/agent-registry.ts`** — Registry client that:\n  - Fetches the full file tree from `msitarzewski/agency-agents` via GitHub API\n  - Parses agent Markdown files (YAML frontmatter with `name`, `description`, `color`, `emoji`, `vibe` + body)\n  - Caches agents locally in `.wombo/agent-cache/` with configurable TTL (24h default)\n  - Supports offline mode using cached agents\n  - Provides `listRegistryAgents()`, `getRegistryAgent()`, `searchRegistryAgents()`, `isRegistryCacheAvailable()`, `isAgentCached()`\n\n- **`src/lib/agent-converter.ts`** — Format converter that:\n  - Converts agency-agents MD format to woco's wave-worker.md template format\n  - Generates proper opencode-compatible YAML frontmatter (`description`, `mode: primary`)\n  - Merges the agent's specialization/personality with woco's standard operational rules (environment, workflow, commit guidelines, constraints, error recovery)\n  - Adjusts heading levels to nest properly\n  - Provides `getAgentSpecializationContext()` for lighter prompt augmentation\n\n**Modified files:**\n- **`src/config.ts`** — Added `agentRegistry` config section with `repo`, `cacheDir`, and `cacheTtlMs`\n\n### Commit 2: `feat(dynamic-agent-types): add per-feature agent type selection`\n\n**Modified files:**\n- **`src/lib/features.ts`** — Added optional `agent?: string` field to `Feature` interface\n- **`src/lib/templates.ts`** — Added `ensureDynamicAgentDefinition()` (async, fetches + converts + installs) and `resolveAgentName()` (priority: CLI flag → feature field → config default)\n- **`src/lib/launcher.ts`** — Added `agentName` to `LaunchOptions` and `ConflictResolverOptions`, used in `launchHeadless()` and `launchConflictResolver()`\n- **`src/commands/launch.ts`** — Added `agent` to `LaunchCommandOptions`, wired dynamic agent resolution through `cmdLaunch`, `launchWaveHeadless`, `launchSingleHeadless`, and `launchNextQueued`\n- **`src/commands/resume.ts`** — Updated to resolve agent names from feature specs\n- **`src/index.ts`** — Added `--agent` CLI flag parsing and help text\n- **`src/lib/schema.ts`** — Added `--agent` flag to launch command schema for introspection","time":{"start":1773352228146,"end":1773352228146}}}
